 ingredients by half except water and maple syrup. Use 100 g water and 80 g maple syrup and proceed as per above.","Serve Spice-rubbed chicken with a side of <em>Rosemary and thyme polenta chips<\/em>.","If you are using large chicken breasts, you will need to cut each breast into halves lengthways prior to rubbing with spices. This will ensure it is cooked completely through in the cooking times indicated."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","25m","2 portions"]}